- *      0         7        8
- *     | command | Resync |     = 0xc0
- *
- * Since the event is written in big-endian byte order, this works
- * providing bits 56-63 of the event are 0xc0.
- *
- *      56     60  63
- *     | Rsvd | Code |    = 0xc0
- *
- * Which means for convenience the event code is 0xc for all MC
- * generated events.
- */
